This repository contains my XMonad configuration files.

Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/ckl/xmonad-config.git ~/
    cp ~/xmonad-config/xmonad.hs ~/.xmonad/
    cp ~/xmonad-config/conkyrc ~/.xmonad/conkyrc
    cp -r ~/xmonad-config/lib/ ~/.xmonad
    cp -r ~/xmonad-config/bin/* ~/bin/
